10
00:01:36,359 --> 00:01:39,599
-Why?
-Because it was only sex for you.

11
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:46,400
So now you're hooked on him?
That's the deal?

12
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:52,439
No fuckin' way.

13
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:56,359
No fuckin' way, Omar.
Are you fuckin' kidding me right now?

14
00:01:56,439 --> 00:01:59,239
Look, Ander… No. I… I mean-- No, no.

15
00:01:59,319 --> 00:02:00,560
This can't be.

16
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:03,079
Please, man.
I'm fucking confused as hell. Ander!

17
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:06,599
-Let's go to the lake and talk, please.
-To talk about what?

18
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:10,319
