28
00:03:09,439 --> 00:03:11,960
Do you really think
I'd fall for that shit, huh?

29
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:24,759
When I got home,
I made up an excuse

30
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,960
they never even asked for

31
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:29,719
because you and I both know
they didn't care what I'd been doing.

32
00:03:30,639 --> 00:03:34,039
They were just relieved to see you.

33
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,240
Well, yes.

34
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:41,159
And I liked feeling… that sense of relief

35
00:03:41,719 --> 00:03:45,080
because it's the same relief I felt
in that hotel room when you hugged me,

36
00:03:45,599 --> 00:03:47,639
even after everything you saw.

37
00:04:07,199 --> 00:04:08,479
No, wait up.

38
00:04:10,919 --> 00:04:12,240
Come here.

39
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:25,240
Don't ever do that to me again.

40
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,680
Have you seen Ari?

41
00:04:45,519 --> 00:04:48,279
She told me
she would meet me here.

42
00:05:08,079 --> 00:05:10,600
I would start
with a more personal approach,

43
00:05:11,639 --> 00:05:13,319
then I'd go to the data.

44
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,199
Because data is boring.

45
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:20,000
It's really our emotions
that transcends it all.

46
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:29,319
EMOTIONAL INTELLIGENCE

47
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,720
How was your weekend?

48
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:50,360
-Uh, good. It was pretty nice out.
-Yeah.

49
00:05:52,399 --> 00:05:54,279
How's Mencía? Did she open up?

50
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:59,600
-No. With her, it's best not to talk.
-Right.

51
00:06:02,319 --> 00:06:03,560
Okay.

52
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:08,160
-All right, show me what you got.
-Okay.

53
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:10,439
No, no. Stay right there.
You're fine where you are.

54
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:16,560
I can go first if you want.
I'm really eager to.

55
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,319
Very well.

56
00:06:25,279 --> 00:06:29,319
