as the three of you here.

226
00:21:16,920 --> 00:21:19,960
I'm the one who's competing with Samuel,
Guzmán, not you.

227
00:21:20,039 --> 00:21:21,440
-Me?
-Yeah.

228
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:24,759
I wasn't. I'm not worried.

229
00:21:24,839 --> 00:21:26,799
